"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**Black Friday DJI Mini 2 deals have arrived, compare all the top Black Friday DJI Mavic drone savings listed below**\\n\\nNovember 22, 2021 08:40 AM Eastern Standard Time\\n\\nBOSTON--([BUSINESS WIRE](https://www.businesswire.com/))--Here’s our review of all the best DJI Mini 2 deals for Black Friday, together with offers on top-rated Mavic quadcopters. Links to the latest deals are listed below.\\n\\n**Best DJI Mini 2 deals:**\\n\\n* **[Save up to $130 on DJI Mini 2 drones at Walmart](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3vSLoal&esheet=52534336&newsitemid=20211122005258&lan=en-US&anchor=Save+up+to+%24130+on+DJI+Mini+2+drones+at+Walmart&index=1&md5=98d6f0513c562c4be7d9af9de41ba7a5)** - check the latest deals on the ultra portable DJI Mini 2, including Fly More Combo bundles, accessories, parts and more\\n* **[Save up to $100 on DJI Mini 2 ultralight drones at Amazon.com -](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fgeni.us%2FgrjvM&esheet=52534336&newsitemid=20211122005258&lan=en-US&anchor=Save+up+to+%24100+on+DJI+Mini+2+ultralight+drones+at+Amazon.com+-&index=2&md5=da7afdda33b55da3f14bef7a8f930456)** featuring Fly More Combo kits for the foldable DJI Mini 2\\n* **[Save on DJI Mini 2 drones at BHPhotoVideo.com](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Ffave.co%2F3mmu7TN&esheet=52534336&newsitemid=20211122005258&lan=en-US&anchor=Save+on+DJI+Mini+2+drones+at+BHPhotoVideo.com&index=3&md5=28e86c4a49317bd0b0a414c95e1c5fac)** - check live prices on these highly rated compact foldable drones from DJI\\n* **[Save on the ultralight and foldable DJI Mini 2 at DJI.com](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fclick.dji.com%2FAI8ZznBIKS6P5GZplDN__g%3Fpm%3Dcustom&esheet=52534336&newsitemid=20211122005258&lan=en-US&anchor=Save+on+the+ultralight+and+foldable+DJI+Mini+2+at+DJI.com&index=4&md5=ef61bc141de49dc8c8641b64f15d3138)** - the DJI Mini 2 wei